Why 14/25: Micron reports clear measurable impacts (11% scope 1 reduction, major renewable procurements, major increases in water reuse and waste recovery, and product energy savings). However, company‑wide emissions reductions remain moderate (not yet in the >25–50% or >50% bands), so the measurable impact is solid but not transformational at scale yet.

